investigation was in progress and that the suspect would soon be charged to court. Speaking to NAN while in custody, Bala said he came to Rikina village from Zamfara and was assisted and sheltered by the children’s parents. The suspect confirmed engaging the children in homosexuality as they mostly sleep together in the night. He attributed the incident to satanic move, adding that he was introduced into homosexuality acts by somebody when he was in Niger and continue with act as a source of pleasure. One of the victims named withheld, told NAN that he was 14 years in primary 4 at Rikina Primary School. The victim said the suspect traced them on their various sleeping places. The victim said he, along with others, mostly woke up in the morning to notice sperm on their backs as some of their trousers were tore or removed by the victim while they are asleep. A parent, who pleaded anonymity, told Newsmen that the case had earlier been reported to the local Hisbah Officials before taking over by NAPTIP. He said the incident was devastating as the suspect was considered as member of the community with all forms of assistance rendered to him. Vanguard News Nigeria The National Agency for the Prohibition of Trafficking in Persons (NAPTIP) has arrested a 21-year-old gay boy who is a house help, Usman Abubakar for allegedly sodomising 10 minors in Sokoto. The Sokoto Zonal Commander of NAPTIP, Mr Hassan Tahir, who disclosed this to newsmen on Thursday, said all the… September 20, 2019 In "News" Officers and men from the Sokoto zonal office of the National Agency for the Prohibition of Traffic in Persons, NAPTIP, have nabbed a 45-year-old woman (names withheld) with 35 children in Zamfara State. June 15, 2012 In "News" Alhaji Bello Danjumu’a, the father of an underage girl, Hauwa’u, who was allegedly abducted for 34 days and sexually abused, has appealed to the authorities to ensure justice on the issue. February 10, 2020 In "News"